            <li><a href="#features" class="hover:text-white transition-colors duration-300">機能比較</a></li>
            <li><a href="#performance" class="hover:text-white transition-colors duration-300">パフォーマンス保証</a></li>
            <li><a href="#dx-package" class="hover:text-white transition-colors duration-300">DXパッケージ</a></li>
